reviews.text: Starbucks at United Centre Admiralty having my breakfast first before going to Philippine consulate... they only hv 4 small round tables here bec the space isn't big enough
Starbucks always know where to locate. This is a good place for a quick break from shopping in the middle of busy street. The coffee is light as usual, but that’s alright.
Good place for a casual work meeting. Nice decor, good amount of space between tables and less crowded than other coffee shops in Central.
A good place to have coffee in the middle of the busy city

This Starbucks up the escalator on the second floor is my go to place whenever I'm in the Central district neighborhood.
Why?  Spacious including a huge backyard like terrace that's almost like a retreat where you are surrounded by skyscrapers, a rare thing in the concrete jungle of HK island.
Clean western toilet (with toilet paper), another rarity.  Sit as long as you want in the hustle and bustle of Central and the mass of humanity down down below.

reviews.text: 好👌

6년만에 다시 찾은 스벅
테이블이 더 생기고 좁아진 느낌! 그래도 2층이라  밝아서 좋아요
바닐라콜드브루 시켰는데 얼음녹은커피같은 맛에요🤪 다른거 시킬껄..😖

Starbucks畀我嘅好處就係 有個聚腳點
